     "VEGETATION as a CLASS has a real signature - a dry, bright, broadband, HF-dominated stochastic RUSTLE: dense unresolvable micro-events, very high zero_crossings_per_second, high spectral_flatness, high centroid, almost no energy below 200 Hz, low crest factor. That is measurable, and it usefully rules out tonal, impulsive and low-frequency material. The SUBCATEGORIES, however, are botany.",
